    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>This endpoint retrieves all issue ratings for a specific role.</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET /roles/&lt;roleId&gt;/issue-ratings</code></p>
<h2 id='rating-creation'>Rating Creation</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Development Time"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"description"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Rating description"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"coefficient"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">-1</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>This endpoint creates a new issue rating.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-2'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>POST /roles/&lt;roleId&gt;/issue-ratings</code> </p>
<h3 id='available-parameters'>Available Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>name</td>
<td>Rating name</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>description</td>
<td>Rating description</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>coefficient</td>
<td>Rating coefficient</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='rating-updating'>Rating Updating</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>The above command returns JSON structured like this:</p>
</blockquote>

<pre class="highlight json tab-json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Development Time"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"description"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"Rating description"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="s2">"coefficient"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">-1</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<p>This endpoint updates an exist issue rating.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-3'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>PUT /roles/&lt;roleId&gt;/issue-ratings/&lt;ID&gt;</code> </p>
<h3 id='available-parameters-2'>Available Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>name</td>
<td>Rating name</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>description</td>
<td>Rating description</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>coefficient</td>
<td>Rating coefficient</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id='rating-deleting'>Rating Deleting</h2>
<p>This endpoint removes an exist issue rating.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-4'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>DELETE /roles/&lt;roleId&gt;/issue-ratings/&lt;ID&gt;</code> </p>
